sourcesContent: import React, { FC, useState } from 'react' import { foodType } from '../../../types' import { useSelector } from 'react-redux' import { RootState } from '../../../store/store' interface ButtonOrderProps{ onAddOrder: (product: foodType) => void product:foodType } const ButtonOrder:FC = ({onAddOrder, product}) => { const order = useSelector((state:RootState) => state.order.userOrder) const handleProductAdd = (event: React.FormEvent, product: foodType) => { event.preventDefault() onAddOrder() console.log(order) } return ( ) } export default ButtonOrder
